        "content": "<p>Hi everyone! I'm just getting started with lean and trying to learn by implementing some simple proofs from my elementary number theory book. I'd appreciate any feedback on <a href=\"https://github.com/Quantum64/lean-projects/blob/main/NumberTheory/dta11.lean#L53\">this proof</a> or any advice for improving my code quality and conciseness.</p>\n<p>Here's the theorem I proved:<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/qCIS5zYDeja_a3kYZhBvpVI7/SCR-20250107-tyla.png\">SCR-20250107-tyla.png</a><br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/MtLRL8PVlhT_G5WNUTfJdbXa/SCR-20250107-tyoj.png\">SCR-20250107-tyoj.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/qCIS5zYDeja_a3kYZhBvpVI7/SCR-20250107-tyla.png\" title=\"SCR-20250107-tyla.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"1214x512\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/qCIS5zYDeja_a3kYZhBvpVI7/SCR-20250107-tyla.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/MtLRL8PVlhT_G5WNUTfJdbXa/SCR-20250107-tyoj.png\" title=\"SCR-20250107-tyoj.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"1160x412\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/MtLRL8PVlhT_G5WNUTfJdbXa/SCR-20250107-tyoj.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
